{"tid":516374,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［連登有愛］求分析辭職去留","createTime":"2018-01-01T11:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T16:31:36.000Z","uid":42499,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"77bc004d2f47c13f1d5e6cc1d25d8ca1a7e7fd2f","tid":516374,"uid":42499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T11:10:11.000Z","msg":"宜家做緊呢份工算係第一份工<br />\n16年9月入職做左一年半到<br />\n大機構黎嘅<br />\n初初只係打雜 人工萬三左右<br />\n但起碼日日準時放工 無乜野要帶返屋企做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後岩岩8月轉左正職 人工二萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做緊一個唔係自己專長同範疇嘅職位<br />\n每一日返幾多點都係留到7點幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n星期六就返長短週 <br />\n但even短週有時都要返去做埋啲手尾<br />\n好多額外paperwork 要帶返屋企做 OT完全無補水<br />\n所以星期六日都係預左有一日半日要做學校野<br />\n平日仲要處理同學生關係 跟進學生資料<br />\n仲有準備學生需要用既材料<br />\n每月開會 做佈置 同家長溝通<br />\n學校仲會要求每年有最低進修時數但無資助<br />\n又會度盡你返工嘅時間要你去做培訓 但多數培訓會超時或者早到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要轉咗正職之後同屋企人 另一半嘈多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返呢份工起碼都每個月病一次 睇一次醫生<br />\n做到身心疲累無咗自己生活同時間咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n福利就一年18日AL 紅日會放 每月可儲2日有薪SL<br />\n但同行其他AL應該更多<br />\n<br />\n宜家做到日日都想喊想走<br />\n但又唔想不負責任掉低班學生<br />\n因為學校遲啲會QR<br />\n我辭職要兩個月通知期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上呢行 呢個時間走未必搵到工<br />\n去其他學校再in未必咁睇好我份cv<br />\n需要各位比啲意見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正評 走啦 呢啲濕鳩學校<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負評 少少事都捱唔到 捱埋去啦廢材"},{"pid":"ae11a2a2a6d2298dfd85e5f33a2b58fa26e7ce11","tid":516374,"uid":22329,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T11:20:20.000Z","msg":"講咁多，都唔知你做乜post,<br />\n<br />\n靜係睇人工，你走左搵得返呢個價咩？"},{"pid":"9ccae92f008abcfb7cf15d523351c734b2f2df4e","tid":516374,"uid":42499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae11a2a2a6d2298dfd85e5f33a2b58fa26e7ce11","tid":516374,"uid":22329,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T11:20:20.000Z","msg":"講咁多，都唔知你做乜post,<br />\n<br />\n靜係睇人工，你走左搵得返呢個價咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T11:44:48.000Z","msg":"宜家入行最低兩萬係基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主要宜家workload太大 宜家心理好唔平衝<br />\n返到屋企做做下野會喊 日日都想辭職<br />\n但唔想不負責任咁走咗去 過唔到自己嗰關<br />\n因為班學生會好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb609bfade8e4daf5047664cca40fc9c76256ba","tid":516374,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T11:54:06.000Z","msg":"幼教？"},{"pid":"5a88aab25b4f77f6b93d51f60a9c7a760eaf5714","tid":516374,"uid":42499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cb609bfade8e4daf5047664cca40fc9c76256ba","tid":516374,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T11:54:06.000Z","msg":"幼教？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:03:14.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baaafc0e9ab4e24a8df317d949b9e72ae9acfae5","tid":516374,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:10:48.000Z","msg":"教育workload一向大<br />\n星期六日帶隊去camp，日日chur住改簿等閒事<br />\n間間都差不多"},{"pid":"1c925f27af81a472ded16d454a99d3af5669d047","tid":516374,"uid":42499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baaafc0e9ab4e24a8df317d949b9e72ae9acfae5","tid":516374,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:10:48.000Z","msg":"教育workload一向大<br />\n星期六日帶隊去camp，日日chur住改簿等閒事<br />\n間間都差不多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:18:23.000Z","msg":"明白嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小學 中學我唔太清楚<br />\n不過唔知係咪機構模式問題<br />\n我覺得自己學唔到野 係到虛度光陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我個職位範疇好狹窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話學到野 咁辛苦都無所謂嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17014055271cdafb123d49b2f2cd88f1e6cee862","tid":516374,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c925f27af81a472ded16d454a99d3af5669d047","tid":516374,"uid":42499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baaafc0e9ab4e24a8df317d949b9e72ae9acfae5","tid":516374,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:10:48.000Z","msg":"教育workload一向大<br />\n星期六日帶隊去camp，日日chur住改簿等閒事<br />\n間間都差不多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:18:23.000Z","msg":"明白嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小學 中學我唔太清楚<br />\n不過唔知係咪機構模式問題<br />\n我覺得自己學唔到野 係到虛度光陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我個職位範疇好狹窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話學到野 咁辛苦都無所謂嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:42:50.000Z","msg":"出黎做野 係叫你output<br />\n想學野只有一係主動問或者偷師<br />\n二係去讀course"},{"pid":"7d73cf6a638ce722c79558f0ad507736e88a5422","tid":516374,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"我再睇返你d comment主要都是workload問題<br />\n你可以試下轉學校ge，但唔好期望太高<br />\n我反而奇怪workload個重量應該實習時感受到，見其他正職教師有同佢地傾開都知唔輕<br />\n除非你做果間校政唔同，但呢d好做位點會有人走，return offer都幾難有"},{"pid":"f105a049700fdadf3bb9487fcd66f43bd6cb00fa","tid":516374,"uid":42499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d73cf6a638ce722c79558f0ad507736e88a5422","tid":516374,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"我再睇返你d comment主要都是workload問題<br />\n你可以試下轉學校ge，但唔好期望太高<br />\n我反而奇怪workload個重量應該實習時感受到，見其他正職教師有同佢地傾開都知唔輕<br />\n除非你做果間校政唔同，但呢d好做位點會有人走，return offer都幾難有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:02:44.000Z","msg":"實習嘅時候當然知道呢行大概個workload<br />\n相比起同行朋友個個都無我咁誇張走咁晏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家做嘅學校校政同教學模式同其他普通學校唔同<br />\n其實我已經有呢個打算轉學校<br />\n但問題係我應該幾時走好<br />\n諗緊頂硬上食埋佢個QR拎經驗完左學年先走定即走放過自己好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：呢個位就係有人走但無人頂之後搵我頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4425880b6749f21be522bb35fbc8133cc1326d2d","tid":516374,"uid":74331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f105a049700fdadf3bb9487fcd66f43bd6cb00fa","tid":516374,"uid":42499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d73cf6a638ce722c79558f0ad507736e88a5422","tid":516374,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"我再睇返你d comment主要都是workload問題<br />\n你可以試下轉學校ge，但唔好期望太高<br />\n我反而奇怪workload個重量應該實習時感受到，見其他正職教師有同佢地傾開都知唔輕<br />\n除非你做果間校政唔同，但呢d好做位點會有人走，return offer都幾難有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:02:44.000Z","msg":"實習嘅時候當然知道呢行大概個workload<br />\n相比起同行朋友個個都無我咁誇張走咁晏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家做嘅學校校政同教學模式同其他普通學校唔同<br />\n其實我已經有呢個打算轉學校<br />\n但問題係我應該幾時走好<br />\n諗緊頂硬上食埋佢個QR拎經驗完左學年先走定即走放過自己好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：呢個位就係有人走但無人頂之後搵我頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:31:36.000Z","msg":"樓主我個情況同你一樣(不過唔係幼教)<br />\n我明白果種人都未適應，工作就接踵而來既無力感(仲要面對esr....)<br />\n不過點都捱埋個新年先開始揾啦，而家你想揾都未有post住，同埋呢行中離真係大忌<br />\n我就打算7月quit既"}]}